{"items":[{"id":"a50124e1-a8f0-408d-ae3b-e1a8fb1af970","text":"The words 'tighten' and 'spot' should never be used in marketing content; instead, prefer specific verbs like 'identify', 'reduce', 'cap', or 'limit'. | To use more specific and impactful language.","context":"marketing writing style correction","date":"2026-04-10T09:30:14.794668+00:00","fact_type":"world","mentioned_at":"2026-04-10T09:30:14.794668+00:00","occurred_start":null,"occurred_end":null,"entities":"tighten, spot, identify, reduce, cap, limit","chunk_id":"marketing-writing_536e118e-2c3b-4a6e-8d98-a4f8d0cba8c6_0","proof_count":1,"tags":[]},{"id":"b789d4b3-2037-449a-8ea3-46fffc827e12","text":"All numbers in marketing content must be written using digits, not spelled out.","context":"marketing writing style correction","date":"2026-04-10T09:30:14.784668+00:00","fact_type":"world","mentioned_at":"2026-04-10T09:30:14.784668+00:00","occurred_start":null,"occurred_end":null,"entities":"numbers","chunk_id":"marketing-writing_536e118e-2c3b-4a6e-8d98-a4f8d0cba8c6_0","proof_count":1,"tags":[]},{"id":"0b8a6c5f-fa7d-4e07-a125-ae027f416883","text":"When listing two or more speakers in marketing content, use their actual names and titles; if names are unknown, the user should be asked.","context":"marketing writing style correction","date":"2026-04-10T09:30:14.774668+00:00","fact_type":"world","mentioned_at":"2026-04-10T09:30:14.774668+00:00","occurred_start":null,"occurred_end":null,"entities":"titles, speakers","chunk_id":"marketing-writing_536e118e-2c3b-4a6e-8d98-a4f8d0cba8c6_0","proof_count":1,"tags":[]},{"id":"2f622f65-eec2-425a-a3be-1f3076530a9c","text":"For webinar/event marketing posts, the date and time should be on its own line in the format 'Tuesday Apr 14, 2pm ET' to ensure scannability. | To make the information scannable for the audience.","context":"marketing writing style correction","date":"2026-04-10T09:30:14.764668+00:00","fact_type":"world","mentioned_at":"2026-04-10T09:30:14.764668+00:00","occurred_start":null,"occurred_end":null,"entities":"date and time format, webinar/event marketing posts","chunk_id":"marketing-writing_536e118e-2c3b-4a6e-8d98-a4f8d0cba8c6_0","proof_count":1,"tags":[]},{"id":"ad1bec0c-efc4-4323-bbcf-c36873170b08","text":"In marketing posts, instead of explicitly thanking people, describe what the community did (e.g., broke it, improved it, opened PRs, filed issues).","context":"","date":"2026-04-10T09:28:51.163291+00:00","fact_type":"observation","mentioned_at":"2026-04-10T09:28:51.163291+00:00","occurred_start":null,"occurred_end":null,"entities":"","chunk_id":null,"proof_count":1,"tags":[]},{"id":"2139d064-6f5b-4ace-9a56-bc82f6a351e9","text":"In marketing posts, instead of explicitly thanking people, describe what the community did (e.g., broke it, improved it, opened PRs, filed issues). | To acknowledge community contributions without using generic thanks.","context":"marketing writing style correction","date":"2026-04-10T09:28:51.163291+00:00","fact_type":"world","mentioned_at":"2026-04-10T09:28:51.163291+00:00","occurred_start":null,"occurred_end":null,"entities":"community, marketing posts","chunk_id":"marketing-writing_b03330ee-2fba-48fe-a412-f1b9bfcba758_0","proof_count":1,"tags":[]},{"id":"68b97706-61b2-4e96-add2-de00c38ddfe2","text":"The word 'just' must never be used in marketing posts.","context":"marketing writing style correction","date":"2026-04-10T09:28:51.153291+00:00","fact_type":"world","mentioned_at":"2026-04-10T09:28:51.153291+00:00","occurred_start":null,"occurred_end":null,"entities":"marketing posts","chunk_id":"marketing-writing_b03330ee-2fba-48fe-a412-f1b9bfcba758_0","proof_count":1,"tags":[]},{"id":"243eb9ea-d9d8-42a3-b0ab-751e2d8e1651","text":"Marketing posts must avoid the banned words: thrilled, excited, delighted, game-changer, revolutionary, leverage, synergy, and just.","context":"","date":"2026-04-10T09:26:48.303368+00:00","fact_type":"observation","mentioned_at":"2026-04-10T09:28:51.153291+00:00","occurred_start":null,"occurred_end":null,"entities":"","chunk_id":null,"proof_count":2,"tags":[]},{"id":"557858d0-71fc-4a14-8a6f-893b98c568fd","text":"For milestone marketing posts, the first line must lead with a provocative claim about what the milestone means for the audience, and the metric should be mentioned in the second sentence.","context":"","date":"2026-04-10T09:28:51.143291+00:00","fact_type":"observation","mentioned_at":"2026-04-10T09:28:51.143291+00:00","occurred_start":null,"occurred_end":null,"entities":"","chunk_id":null,"proof_count":1,"tags":[]},{"id":"07c47fc2-cb11-4ed0-8e58-4b159996dc7d","text":"For milestone marketing posts, the first line must lead with a provocative claim about what the milestone means for the audience, and the metric should be mentioned in the second sentence. | To engage the audience effectively before revealing the metric.","context":"marketing writing style correction","date":"2026-04-10T09:28:51.143291+00:00","fact_type":"world","mentioned_at":"2026-04-10T09:28:51.143291+00:00","occurred_start":null,"occurred_end":null,"entities":"milestone marketing posts, audience","chunk_id":"marketing-writing_b03330ee-2fba-48fe-a412-f1b9bfcba758_0","proof_count":1,"tags":[]},{"id":"9546f8d6-bf05-4189-b6f4-57b44d5c06be","text":"For new product or feature announcements, a concrete metric or outcome must be included in the second sentence.","context":"","date":"2026-04-10T09:27:50.970923+00:00","fact_type":"observation","mentioned_at":"2026-04-10T09:27:50.970923+00:00","occurred_start":null,"occurred_end":null,"entities":"","chunk_id":null,"proof_count":1,"tags":[]},{"id":"ec5ddffa-1d07-4bb9-92ad-ab79e5473234","text":"For new product or feature announcements, a concrete metric or outcome must be included in the second sentence.","context":"marketing writing style correction","date":"2026-04-10T09:27:50.970923+00:00","fact_type":"world","mentioned_at":"2026-04-10T09:27:50.970923+00:00","occurred_start":null,"occurred_end":null,"entities":"new product announcements, outcome, feature announcements, concrete metric","chunk_id":"marketing-writing_6cfaa08d-c061-4a6f-ad1b-339779bbe1ba_0","proof_count":1,"tags":[]},{"id":"f3d776d9-8747-40e5-9fbb-b86bfb2760e2","text":"The closing question in marketing posts must come on its own line after the signature.","context":"marketing writing style correction","date":"2026-04-10T09:27:50.960923+00:00","fact_type":"world","mentioned_at":"2026-04-10T09:27:50.960923+00:00","occurred_start":null,"occurred_end":null,"entities":"signature, marketing posts, closing question","chunk_id":"marketing-writing_6cfaa08d-c061-4a6f-ad1b-339779bbe1ba_0","proof_count":1,"tags":[]},{"id":"705e8ff3-8c9c-4ae4-aefd-a4a44d8d77ca","text":"Marketing posts must always end with a single open-ended question, which must come on its own line after the signature.","context":"","date":"2026-04-10T09:26:48.333368+00:00","fact_type":"observation","mentioned_at":"2026-04-10T09:27:50.960923+00:00","occurred_start":null,"occurred_end":null,"entities":"","chunk_id":null,"proof_count":2,"tags":[]},{"id":"290a41ba-2a8d-4e23-b78e-58e4504c9e27","text":"For future marketing posts, the signature must be on its own line at the very end, formatted as '— the team', with a blank line preceding it.","context":"marketing writing style correction","date":"2026-04-10T09:27:50.950923+00:00","fact_type":"world","mentioned_at":"2026-04-10T09:27:50.950923+00:00","occurred_start":null,"occurred_end":null,"entities":"signature, marketing posts","chunk_id":"marketing-writing_6cfaa08d-c061-4a6f-ad1b-339779bbe1ba_0","proof_count":1,"tags":[]},{"id":"acda6d0d-0a40-42c1-a5e4-7e0f36d36601","text":"Marketing posts should not use first-person pronouns ('I' or 'we'). The signature must be on its own line at the very end, formatted as '— the team', with a blank line preceding it.","context":"","date":"2026-04-10T09:26:48.313368+00:00","fact_type":"observation","mentioned_at":"2026-04-10T09:27:50.950923+00:00","occurred_start":null,"occurred_end":null,"entities":"","chunk_id":null,"proof_count":2,"tags":[]},{"id":"c78b6144-1c2d-41a1-b067-54d29445f7c8","text":"Marketing posts must always end with a single open-ended question.","context":"marketing writing style preference","date":"2026-04-10T09:26:48.333368+00:00","fact_type":"world","mentioned_at":"2026-04-10T09:26:48.333368+00:00","occurred_start":null,"occurred_end":null,"entities":"marketing posts","chunk_id":"marketing-writing_2d834178-fb47-4969-b7e8-d7b0338baa0e_0","proof_count":1,"tags":[]},{"id":"f743d37a-45a0-41e1-b8d5-f4d8a32d961a","text":"Marketing posts must never use hashtags.","context":"","date":"2026-04-10T09:26:48.323368+00:00","fact_type":"observation","mentioned_at":"2026-04-10T09:26:48.323368+00:00","occurred_start":null,"occurred_end":null,"entities":"","chunk_id":null,"proof_count":1,"tags":[]},{"id":"6c9fd5fb-803a-4bd3-a55b-40100f1211fa","text":"Marketing posts must never use hashtags.","context":"marketing writing style preference","date":"2026-04-10T09:26:48.323368+00:00","fact_type":"world","mentioned_at":"2026-04-10T09:26:48.323368+00:00","occurred_start":null,"occurred_end":null,"entities":"hashtags","chunk_id":"marketing-writing_2d834178-fb47-4969-b7e8-d7b0338baa0e_0","proof_count":1,"tags":[]},{"id":"328afabc-2fb8-40ff-9615-9258bc87d58c","text":"Marketing posts should not use first-person pronouns 'I' or 'we', and should be signed as 'the team'.","context":"marketing writing style preference","date":"2026-04-10T09:26:48.313368+00:00","fact_type":"world","mentioned_at":"2026-04-10T09:26:48.313368+00:00","occurred_start":null,"occurred_end":null,"entities":"marketing posts","chunk_id":"marketing-writing_2d834178-fb47-4969-b7e8-d7b0338baa0e_0","proof_count":1,"tags":[]},{"id":"72a77271-47da-4deb-a5b9-27792bdb2ea9","text":"Marketing posts must avoid the banned words: thrilled, excited, delighted, game-changer, revolutionary, leverage, and synergy.","context":"marketing writing style preference","date":"2026-04-10T09:26:48.303368+00:00","fact_type":"world","mentioned_at":"2026-04-10T09:26:48.303368+00:00","occurred_start":null,"occurred_end":null,"entities":"marketing posts","chunk_id":"marketing-writing_2d834178-fb47-4969-b7e8-d7b0338baa0e_0","proof_count":1,"tags":[]},{"id":"38239837-bd81-45e7-8a34-9e9b3ba53d45","text":"Marketing posts should not include emojis.","context":"","date":"2026-04-10T09:26:48.293368+00:00","fact_type":"observation","mentioned_at":"2026-04-10T09:26:48.293368+00:00","occurred_start":null,"occurred_end":null,"entities":"","chunk_id":null,"proof_count":1,"tags":[]},{"id":"40072054-e99d-41a5-ad2b-b71e2e3dace7","text":"Marketing posts should not include emojis.","context":"marketing writing style preference","date":"2026-04-10T09:26:48.293368+00:00","fact_type":"world","mentioned_at":"2026-04-10T09:26:48.293368+00:00","occurred_start":null,"occurred_end":null,"entities":"emojis","chunk_id":"marketing-writing_2d834178-fb47-4969-b7e8-d7b0338baa0e_0","proof_count":1,"tags":[]},{"id":"a2242624-66c5-4760-88b1-4c22cbbf7186","text":"Marketing posts should lead with the user benefit or explain why the content matters.","context":"","date":"2026-04-10T09:26:48.283368+00:00","fact_type":"observation","mentioned_at":"2026-04-10T09:26:48.283368+00:00","occurred_start":null,"occurred_end":null,"entities":"","chunk_id":null,"proof_count":1,"tags":[]},{"id":"fcaf7ff5-dc3f-4173-9855-461b41385faa","text":"Marketing posts should lead with the user benefit or explain why the content matters.","context":"marketing writing style preference","date":"2026-04-10T09:26:48.283368+00:00","fact_type":"world","mentioned_at":"2026-04-10T09:26:48.283368+00:00","occurred_start":null,"occurred_end":null,"entities":"marketing posts","chunk_id":"marketing-writing_2d834178-fb47-4969-b7e8-d7b0338baa0e_0","proof_count":1,"tags":[]},{"id":"04a52c3f-9636-4f58-9e4e-426adcb3ca76","text":"LinkedIn marketing posts must be a maximum of 600 characters and contain a maximum of 4 short paragraphs.","context":"","date":"2026-04-10T09:26:48.273368+00:00","fact_type":"observation","mentioned_at":"2026-04-10T09:26:48.273368+00:00","occurred_start":null,"occurred_end":null,"entities":"","chunk_id":null,"proof_count":1,"tags":[]},{"id":"c77628c7-6715-4280-888c-d670275bcedf","text":"LinkedIn marketing posts must be a maximum of 600 characters and contain a maximum of 4 short paragraphs.","context":"marketing writing style preference","date":"2026-04-10T09:26:48.273368+00:00","fact_type":"world","mentioned_at":"2026-04-10T09:26:48.273368+00:00","occurred_start":null,"occurred_end":null,"entities":"LinkedIn posts","chunk_id":"marketing-writing_2d834178-fb47-4969-b7e8-d7b0338baa0e_0","proof_count":1,"tags":[]},{"id":"52c33aec-2e3e-4223-8968-7cd30a08a41e","text":"The target audience for marketing posts consists of technical leaders, including CTOs, VPs of Engineering, and staff-plus engineers.","context":"","date":"2026-04-10T09:26:48.263368+00:00","fact_type":"observation","mentioned_at":"2026-04-10T09:26:48.263368+00:00","occurred_start":null,"occurred_end":null,"entities":"","chunk_id":null,"proof_count":1,"tags":[]},{"id":"556e3665-eca3-43a6-8964-50e2f727e090","text":"The target audience for marketing posts is technical leaders, including CTOs, VPs of Engineering, and staff-plus engineers.","context":"marketing writing style preference","date":"2026-04-10T09:26:48.263368+00:00","fact_type":"world","mentioned_at":"2026-04-10T09:26:48.263368+00:00","occurred_start":null,"occurred_end":null,"entities":"CTOs, technical leaders, VPs Eng, staff-plus engineers","chunk_id":"marketing-writing_2d834178-fb47-4969-b7e8-d7b0338baa0e_0","proof_count":1,"tags":[]},{"id":"df044c28-ec26-4e21-a978-6e892912d3cf","text":"Marketing posts should avoid corporate buzzwords.","context":"","date":"2026-04-10T09:26:48.253368+00:00","fact_type":"observation","mentioned_at":"2026-04-10T09:26:48.253368+00:00","occurred_start":null,"occurred_end":null,"entities":"","chunk_id":null,"proof_count":1,"tags":[]},{"id":"b1056f19-4588-4296-b90e-fe8667786b2e","text":"Marketing posts should avoid corporate buzzwords.","context":"marketing writing style preference","date":"2026-04-10T09:26:48.253368+00:00","fact_type":"world","mentioned_at":"2026-04-10T09:26:48.253368+00:00","occurred_start":null,"occurred_end":null,"entities":"marketing posts","chunk_id":"marketing-writing_2d834178-fb47-4969-b7e8-d7b0338baa0e_0","proof_count":1,"tags":[]},{"id":"360ec0c7-38f4-4385-80f7-7b755fc58c83","text":"Marketing posts should have a confident and direct tone.","context":"","date":"2026-04-10T09:26:48.243368+00:00","fact_type":"observation","mentioned_at":"2026-04-10T09:26:48.243368+00:00","occurred_start":null,"occurred_end":null,"entities":"","chunk_id":null,"proof_count":1,"tags":[]},{"id":"0c682b56-b219-4f2c-9fa8-13da07df1887","text":"User prefers marketing posts to have a confident and direct tone. | Involving: user","context":"marketing writing style preference","date":"2026-04-10T09:26:48.243368+00:00","fact_type":"world","mentioned_at":"2026-04-10T09:26:48.243368+00:00","occurred_start":null,"occurred_end":null,"entities":"marketing posts","chunk_id":"marketing-writing_2d834178-fb47-4969-b7e8-d7b0338baa0e_0","proof_count":1,"tags":[]}],"total":33,"limit":50,"offset":0}